# This lab uses Cosign keyless signing with GitHub Actions OIDC.
# There is no long-lived public/private key pair to commit.
#
# Verification is configured in policies/cluster-image-policy.yaml with:
# - issuer: https://token.actions.githubusercontent.com
# - subjectRegExp: https://github.com/nguyenha0112/w10_day4_am_lab/.github/workflows/build-push.yml@refs/heads/main
#
# If your instructor requires key-based signing instead, run:
#   cosign generate-key-pair
# Then commit the generated cosign.pub content here and store cosign.key plus COSIGN_PASSWORD in GitHub Secrets.
